                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>The only information found on this meeting is that contained in the Log, <hi
                        rend="italic">ante</hi>, <ref target="#pg_288">p. 288</ref>, which indicates
                    that Churchill joined Roosevelt in the latter’s map room at the Citadel “for a
                    review of the latest war news”. The discussion also included naval problems in
                    the Pacific and the difficulties of supply there.</p>
            </div>
